name: First tandem skydive
description: A Tandem skydive adventure is the free-falling thrill of a lifetime! Almost anyone 18 years of age or older can enjoy a tandem skydive–it’s great for all the adults on your list! Our Tandem Skydive Gift Certificate can be used any day of the week.

name: Delta planing
description: Delta planing is an exfoliating procedure using a straight-edge blade. The treatment will allow products and laser therapies to penetrate the skin more easily

name: GO-KARTING
description: Take the gamble out of gift-giving. Give your champion an Ace Karts gift card.
